snippet.title: Guns and Rush - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2065770/?utm_source=youtube_trailer

Immerse yourself in a post-apocalyptic wasteland in this intense horde combat shooter that combines roguelike and bullet-hell elements. Battle relentless waves of monstrous foes as you strive to survive and conquer challenging levels. In my game no vampire, survive 20 minutes!
